│   return Cmp;                                                │
│ ```                                                          │
│                                                              │
│ The `match` function performs a strict identity check. It    │
│ does not consider `+0.0` and `-0.0` to be the same. When     │
│ `NoSignedZero` is true, a more relaxed check is required     │
